│ incorrectly widens the expression, effectively adding `2^16` to the value, resulting in    │
│ `131048` instead of `65512`.\n\nThe fix is to ensure that when `getSCEVAtScope()` is       │
│ called on an `SCEVConstant`, it simply returns the constant itself, as a constant's value  │
│ is invariant across loop scopes.\n\n### 4. Proposed Edit Point(s)\n\nThe fix is to modify  │
