│ scConstant: {\n  // A constant is a constant, regardless of the new scope.\n  return       │
│ this;\n}\n```\n\nThis change ensures that the function correctly identifies that a         │
│ constant's value does not change when moving to an outer scope, preventing the incorrect   │
│ widening operation.\n\n### 5. Conclusion\n\nBy correcting the logic for `SCEVConstant` in  │
