│ My analysis indicates that the bug lies in how `SCEV::getSCEVAtScope` handles              │
│ `SCEVConstant` expressions. The function incorrectly modifies the constant's value when it │
│ should be treated as invariant across scopes. The fix is to make the `scConstant` case in  │
│ `getSCEVAtScope` simply return the constant itself.                                        │
│                                                                                            │
│ I will now apply this change.                                                              │
│                                                                                            │
│ <tool_call>                                                                                │
│ {                                                                                          │
